o hit the target directly. Included in this group are small flasks of oil, acid, poison, holy water, potions, and boulders. Hurled boulders are included because they bounce and bound along after they hit, leaving a swath of destruction.\000\000Q\000\000\000\032\000\000\000:\211\035\000\355\214\035\0007\000\000\000 >\2004\000\200\000\0004\002\212\230\232\206\0300`\200\001\000\202\343*\352$\334\200\007\000\211\200\001\000\202\377\000\000\000\000Table of Contents\000\000 \000\000^\000\000\000-\000\000\000\234\214\035\000K\215\035\0001\000\000\000\002\260\004\000\000{\006;\000O\201;\000\000\001\000\000\377\377\377\377K\215\035\000\232\301\035\000Range-- Missile Attack (Dungeon Master Guide)\272\002\000\000f\002\000\000\355\214\035\000\021\300\035\000T\000\000\000 v\200\315\004\000\200\000\0004\002\212\230\232\206\0300`\200\005\000\202\200\001\000\202\203\353\021\000\004*~\361\267Players.hlp\000\200\007\000\211\200\001\000\200\013\000\200\001\000\202\203\202\377\000Range\000\000\000\000The first step in making a missile attack is to find the range from the attacker to the target. This is measured in yards from one point to the other and is compared to the range categories for the weapon used (see \000\000Table 45\000\000 in the\000 Player's Handbook\000).\000\000If the distance is greater than the long range given, the target is out of range. If the distance is between the long- and medium-range numbers, the target is at long range. When it is between the medium- and short-range numbers, medium range is used. And when it is equal to or less than the short-range distance, the target is at short ranK\215\035\000\021\300\035\000\355\214\035\000ge.\000\000\211\001\000\000O\001\000\000K\215\035\000\232\301\035\000:\000\000\000 B\200\237\002\000\200\000\0004\002\212\230\232\206\0300`\200\001\000\203\202\202\343*\352$\334\200\007\000\211\200\001\000\202\377\000\000Short-range attacks suffer no range modifier. Medium-range attacks suffer a -2 penalty to the attack roll. Long-ran